          "type": "standalone_richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Sleeping well is as necessary to a healthy lifestyle as eating well or exercising regularly. It is an essential biological function of our body.<br/><br/>Specialists have insisted for years on the importance of sleeping well to ensure physical and psychological health, emphasising how sleep disturbances interfere with daily activities.<br/><br/>When sleep-related problems emerge, you should focus on all the elements that make up your night shelter. Imagine lying in a comfortable bed, wrapped in soft blankets and embraced by a soft light that cradles you. We bet you can’t wait to fall into a deep and relaxing sleep.<br/><br/>Indeed, investing in a good mattress, pillows, and other bed essentials will do wonders. We list down some tips on how to choose the perfect bedding essentials.</p>"
          }
        },
